data.description: Exquisite, custom-designed luxury home situated in the highly desirable Park Place community. This exceptional residence boasts a beautifully crafted basement, offering the ultimate in elegance and refinement. Step inside to discover the breathtaking 10-foot ceilings adorned with exquisite custom crown molding throughout. As you enter the stunning foyer, you'll be greeted by a sophisticated front office featuring elegant glass French doors on your left, while a formal dining room awaits on your right. The coffered-ceiling family room is nothing short of remarkable, featuring a cozy fireplace and built-in bookshelves that perfectly complement the stunning hardwood floors found throughout the home. The main level is a haven of tranquility, with the luxurious primary bedroom offering its own fireplace, an expansive spa-like bathroom adorned with vaulted ceilings, a double vanity, a soaking tub, and a generously sized walk-in closet complete with custom built-ins. Two additional guest bedrooms on the main level ensure ample space for family and friends. Indulge your inner chef in the chef-inspired, open-concept kitchen, expertly designed to create a seamless space for entertaining. The kitchen boasts a spacious island, a separate keeping room with a fireplace, and a convenient butler's pantry. Upstairs, a private suite with its own bath provides a secluded retreat for guests or family members. Prepare to be amazed by the finished basement, a true entertainer's delight. This remarkable space features a fully equipped kitchen, a vast entertainment area, and an additional three bedrooms, including a grand master bedroom and bath. With its own keeping room and fireplace, the basement is perfectly suited to serve as an in-law suite or a luxurious private retreat. Escape the everyday on your private, tranquil covered rear porch, the perfect spot to unwind and enjoy the serenity of your surroundings.
